{"TopicId":214561,"ForumId":198,"TopicTitle":"Saving and loading a craft mid flight distorts the wings","CreatedByName":"Scidleee","CreatedById":227118,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-06T15:42:42Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Scidleee","CreatedById":227118,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-06T15:42:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs seen in this screen shot bellow, when I saved and loaded a plane mid flight, the wings, elevators and tail are bent/ warped out of proportions. It slightly affects the aerodynamics.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1070094209006182400/1082326677771780096/image.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow also my plane just falls apart when i load it...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1070094209006182400/1082327944267042996/image.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Draradech","CreatedById":139656,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-06T22:34:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP2 0.1.0.0.20892 \u00A0 - \u00A0 Windows 10 Home 21H2 \u00A0 - \u00A0 Ryzen 9 3950X \u00A0 - \u00A0 RTX 2080 Ti (Driver 531.18)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan confirm. Can also happen on the runway. Reloading a quicksave repeatedly, about 10% of loads have crumpled wings.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCrumpled\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022z8IHqRx.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022120.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/z8IHqRx.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is how it should look like\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022YtmfSgg.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022120.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/YtmfSgg.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-03-06T22:34:24Z\u0022 title=\u002203/06/2023 10:34  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 6, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Draradech\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}